To wire up your songs:

Put your MP3 files in a folder next to index.html — e.g. assets/music/.
Open the file and find the MUSIC_TRACKS array near the bottom (search for music player). Fill it in like:

jsconst MUSIC_TRACKS = [
  { title: 'Song One', src: 'assets/music/song1.mp3' },
  { title: 'Song Two', src: 'assets/music/song2.mp3' },
];

In sw.js, add those same paths to whatever list it precaches on install, so they're cached offline the first time the app loads — same mechanism your icons and manifest already use.
